                    <p>
                        2021-yili esa <a href="https://tuit.uz/">Toshkent Axborot Texnologiyalari universiteti</a>ning Dasturiy injiniring fakultetiga davlat granti asosida o'qishga qabul qilindim va Dasturlash haqidagi dastlabki tushunchalarga ega bo'ldim :)
                    </p>
                    <code class="badge bg-secondary">Hello World!</code>
                    <br />
                    <br />
                    <h3>#pdp</h3>
                    Ikkinchi kursdan boshlab har xil kurslarga bordim va hayotimni o'zgartirgan joylardan biri <a href="https://online.pdp.uz/">PDP Academy</a> bo'ldi.PDP da Ingliz tili va Dasturlash bo'yicha bilimlar oldim.
                    <br />
                    <br />
                    <div class="pdp d-flex justify-content-center">
                        <img class="rounded border-1" src="~/images/pdp.jpg" />
                    </div>
                    <p class="text-center">#pdp ,english intensive</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="accordion-item">
            <h2 class="accordion-header" id="flush-headingThree">
                <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#flush-collapseThree" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="flush-collapseThree">
                    Experience
                </button>
            </h2>
            <div id="flush-collapseThree" class="accordion-collapse collapse" aria-labelledby="flush-headingThree" data-bs-parent="#accordionFlushExample">
                <div class="accordion-body">
                    Avvaliga <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/elbekdeveloper/">Elbek Normurodov</a> tashkil qilgan <a href="https://github.com/hassanhabib/The-Standard-Uzbek">Standart arxitektura</a>ga yo'naltirilgan kursida o'qish davomida <a href="https://github.com/ElbekDeveloper/CashOverflow">CashOverflow</a> nomli backend dasturini Standart arxitektura asosida qurdik, keyinchalik Tarteeb jamosiga qo'shilib <a href="https://github.com/ElbekDeveloper/Tarteeb">Tarteeb</a> va <a href="https://t.me/TasweerAI_bot">TasweerAI_bot</a> projectlarida ishladim.
                    <br />
                    <br />
                    Vaqt o'tishi bilan <a href="https://www.kdb.uz/uz">KDB bank</a>da Backend Developer sifatida ishlay boshladim.
                </div>
            </div>
